author: Benton Thompson III
title: Benton Thompson III
text: Ms. Kemp has always been very helpful whenever I have a question or request. Her customer service is the good old fashioned type. Where you feel you have an agent that cares about your needs. She knows my voice when I call, which is not regularly. She is always willing to go the extra mile to assist. In this time of discretionary spending where you have multiple choices, she always earns my business time and time again. You buy services from people not companies. Ms. Kemp is who I choose to give my business to.
